住先<br />\n到有返咁上下先試引體上升"},{"pid":"5b80b2165b7e66e7816f907d7f1d3d9ca842fc58","tid":410111,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我覺得做引體上升真係唔易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你宜家咁細力 好難用兩隻手支撐到全身體重<br />\n不如用啞鈴練住先<br />\n到有返咁上下先試引體上升</blockquote><br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c856bfb0e65b5abf4959f8bcdfd516a72d80a1","tid":410111,"uid":77283,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tB3X4TjTIes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtB3X4TjTIes&d=vcHNRl9pa4qkm7TlOwFjSMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=84812b40\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tB3X4TjTIes</a><br />\n引體上升主要用你背隻加少量二頭肌既力拉上去<br />\n但係普遍人都唔識點activate自己背隻既肌肉<br />\n所以初練既時候你應該好似片咁樣搵條矮啲既bar做斜身引體(正手捉，兩隻手應該要闊過膊頭）feel下用背隻力拉<br />\n如果用得岩係會feel到自己背隻會夾實，忌駝背<br />\n如果呢個master左就搵返啲高bar，跳上最頂，下巴過杆，然後慢慢hold住用最長既時間慢慢落黎，繼續activate你既背肌<br />\n勤力練既話應該半個月都練到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(希望我唔會認真左)"},{"pid":"a30d14c94a4dd43a088eee1ec941ca7427c89c0c","tid":410111,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"我163cm，98kg，反手做到2下 ，正手有助跑做到1下"},{"pid":"cd412c72829c21c9a7721e4f8c028dc71134ee8d","tid":410111,"uid":133801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"172cm 45.5kg 男 最多兩下 可以點train?"},{"pid":"64b1385533d3b273800d4e647451863e943e3afd","tid":410111,"uid":72587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:06:51.000Z","msg":"做半下夠 唔係會太大隻"},{"pid":"bbeb77f0bf1cfdab8e055a196defa133c541e596","tid":410111,"uid":72751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我163cm，98kg，反手做到2下 ，正手有助跑做到1下</blockquote><br />\n163 98kg?<br />\n有無相"},{"pid":"c137363a8834